Package ca.utoronto.atrc.web4all.configuration

Interface Summary
SetterLauncher Interface that defines the configuration plug-in API.
 

Class Summary
AbstractSetterLauncher Class that provides the base structure of a SetterLauncher without actually implementing the methods of the interface.
AccLipInfoPackage A package of information based on the contents of an ACCLIP preferences document, and individuated by a type of technology (e.g., a screen reader).
ParameterState Stores state information about a specific third party technology parameter, or setting.
ReadProcessIStreams Read the "stdout" and "stderr" streams of a Process object to insure that they are cleared as they fill up.
SettingsBundle Specialized ResourceBundle that is identified based on an ACCLIP technology type, and that contains a look up table of ParameterState objects.
